cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with multi-image deblurring, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep convolutional neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.MM - Machine Learning). The paper also proposes a new algorithm, which involves learning a comparison function and incremental aggregation, which falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI - Artificial Intelligence) and optimization (cs.GR - Graphics).
